ğŸ¯ Goal

A cloud-based AI platform that:

Lets users upload invoices (PDF, image, or scan)

Automatically extracts text and key data (vendor, total, date, category)

Classifies invoices into categories (e.g., utilities, equipment, supplies)

Exports results to Excel/CSV or integrates with accounting tools (QuickBooks, Google Sheets, etc.)

