| Layer          | Tech                                                             |
| -------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Frontend**   | Next.js (React), TailwindCSS, Axios                              |
| **Backend**    | FastAPI (Python 3.12), Pydantic, SQLAlchemy                      |
| **AI / OCR**   | `docTR` (DeepMind OCR) or `Tesseract`, Hugging Face Transformers |
| **Task Queue** | Celery + Redis                                                   |
| **Database**   | PostgreSQL                                                       |
| **Deployment** | Docker + Docker Compose                                          |
| **CI/CD**      | GitHub Actions                                                   |
| **Tests**      | PyTest                                                           |
| **Docs**       | Swagger / ReDoc auto-generated from FastAPI                      |


